  <div class="hero-inner">
    <h1>Ronnie<br>Bailey</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">A continuous record of how a long-standing interest in language gradually became a broader study of culture, public institutions, and international affairs.</p>
    <p class="french-line">Un parcours consacré aux langues, aux institutions publiques, au patrimoine culturel et aux affaires internationales.</p>
    <div class="hero-links">
      <a href="#timeline">Studies &amp; Engagement</a>
